metadata.description: Guoodle Gang is a collection of 5555 NFTs that have been randomly generated from over 100 billion possible trait combinations.  Our utility system provides sustainable value to our community through decisions made by the holders, 50% of funds raised and 5% of royalties go directly to the community wallet! Owning a Guoodle Gang NFT will serve as an access pass that allows you to submit project applications to our NFT launchpad, enter our private alpha & NFT giveaways, claim free merch and vote on all decisions.
